    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# PH Lead Generation Automation\n\nThis workflow collects dental clinic leads across major cities in the Philippines using Google Maps APIs.  \nIt automatically extracts:\n\n- Clinic Name  \n- Phone Number  \n- Website  \n- Place ID (used for deduplication)  \n\nThe automation removes duplicates, enriches data, and saves everything to Google Sheets.\n\n### How it works:\n1. **Query Generator** provides target search terms (e.g., Imus, Bacoor, Dasma, Las Piñas, Muntinlupa).  \n2. **Google Maps Text Search API** fetches matched clinics.  \n3. **Place Details API** retrieves contact information.  \n4. **Dedupe Logic** prevents adding the same clinic twice.  \n5. **Data Storage** appends new leads to Google Sheets.  \n6. **Daily Schedule Trigger** runs this workflow automatically.\n\nFeel free to update search queries anytime to expand coverage and generate more PH-based leads.\n",
        "height": 512,
        "width": 752
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        320,
        -576
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "1537308d-2ee1-40d0-8b10-789fbae11c0a",
      "name": "Sticky Note"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const services = [\n  \"dentist\",\n  \"dental clinic\",\n  \"orthodontist\",\n  \"pediatric dentist\"\n];\n\nconst locations = [\n  \"imus cavite\",\n  \"bacoor cavite\",\n  \"dasmarinas cavite\",\n  \"las pinas\",\n  \"muntinlupa\",\n  \"zapote\",\n  \"alabang\",\n  \"molino cavite\"\n];\n\nconst modifiers = [\n  \"\",\n  \"near me\",\n  \"24 hours\",\n  \"emergency\",\n  \"family\"\n];\n\nconst queries = [];\n\nfor (const s of services) {\n  for (const l of locations) {\n    for (const m of modifiers) {\n      queries.push(`${s} ${l} ${m}`.trim());\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nreturn queries.map(q => ({ json: { query: q }}));\n"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        -208,
        0
      ],
      "id": "7f39f102-a8b1-4614-9ec6-aea080319302",
      "name": "Generate Dynamic Queries"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Collect all queries from previous node\nconst allQueries = items.map(i => i.json.query);\n\n// Safety check\nif (!allQueries.length) {\n  throw new Error(\"No queries received in Daily Query Rotation\");\n}\n\n// Rotate queries based on day of week (0–6)\nconst dayIndex = new Date().getDay();\n\n// Split queries into 7 buckets\nconst bucketSize = Math.ceil(allQueries.length / 7);\nconst start = dayIndex * bucketSize;\nconst end = start + bucketSize;\n\n// Select today's queries\nconst todaysQueries = allQueries.slice(start, end);\n\n// Output in n8n item format\nreturn todaysQueries.map(q => ({\n  json: { query: q }\n}));\n"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        16,
        0
      ],
      "id": "4f03ee8f-6a52-4f90-96b6-1a4035527db6",
      "name": "Daily Query Rotation"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const output = [];\n\nfor (const item of items) {\n  // Handle all possible n8n response shapes\n  const results =\n    item.json.results ||\n    item.json.body?.results ||\n    item.json.data?.results ||\n    [];\n\n  // Safety: skip if no results\n  if (!Array.isArray(results)) continue;\n\n  for (const r of results) {\n    if (!r.place_id) continue;\n\n    output.push({\n      json: {\n        name: r.name || null,\n        address: r.formatted_address || null,\n        place_id: r.place_id,\n        rating: r.rating ?? null\n      }\n    });\n  }\n}\n\nreturn output;\n"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        416,
        0
      ],
      "id": "c55dcb65-9e35-4992-90d8-ee43a8dfe6e5",
      "name": "Code (extract + flatten place_id)"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const LIMIT = 150;\nreturn items.slice(0, LIMIT);\n"
      },
